room_title: Escape room "Walkers" by Great Escape Delaware in Newark
room_description:
The zombie apocalypse has finally happened! You've been able to survive by banding together with a tight group of other survivors. While on the run, you've come across signs for a sanctuary location. You seek shelter but encounter another group of survivors who capture you and lock you up in cages. You quickly learn they have adopted cannibalism due to a shortage of food!
While you are locked up, the site begins to be overrun by a huge group of zombies. Now is your chance to escape! Can you get out before they return or even worse, before the zombies attack?
